query:
SELECT pwi.id, pwi.productId, pwi.batch, la.labelCode, la.id as label_id
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
LEFT JOIN labelAssociations la ON la.productId = pwi.productId AND la.batch = pwi.batch
WHERE pwi.waveId = 3 AND pwi.productSku = '834207';
